### Address Management Endpoints

### Get User Addresses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Save New Address
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "id": "addr-123",
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "street": "123 Main St",
  "city": "New York",
  "state": "NY",
  "zip_code": "10001",
  "type": "home",
  "address": "123 Main St, Apt 4B",
  "apartment": "Apt 4B",
  "title": "Home Address",
  "latitude": 40.7128,
  "longitude": -74.0060,
  "is_default": true
}

###

### Update Address
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses/addr-123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "street": "456 Oak Ave",
  "apartment": "Suite 2A",
  "title": "Updated Home Address"
}

###

### Delete Address
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses/addr-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Default Address
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses/default
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Set Default Address
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses/addr-123/set-default
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Address Stream (Not Implemented - WebSocket)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/addresses/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

